  "_version": "1.0",
  "_notes": [
    "SDT Detection Rules — edit freely, no Python knowledge required.",
    "All keyword matching is case-insensitive substring match.",
    "security_products: first match wins per category — put more specific entries first.",
    "service_keywords: all matches bucket the service — order does not matter.",
    "Per-session override: place a detection_rules.json in the session folder.",
    "  Session rules are ADDITIVE — they append to the global list, not replace it.",
    "  To add a custom product per-engagement, just add it to the session copy."
